msgid "Welcome to LMCache!"
msgstr "欢迎使用 LMCache！"

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
msgid "LMCache"
msgstr "LMCache"

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
msgid "**Supercharge Your LLM with the Fastest KV Cache Layer.**"
msgstr "**用最快的 KV Cache 层为您的 LLM 提供强大支持。**"

#: ../../source/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"We are currently in the process of upgrading our documentation to provide"
" better guidance and examples. Some sections may be under construction. "
"Thank you for your patience!"
msgstr "我们目前正在升级我们的文档，以提供更好的指导和示例。某些部分可能正在建设中。感谢您的耐心等待！"

#: ../../source/index.rst:36
msgid ""
"LMCache lets LLMs prefill each text only once. By storing the KV caches "
"of all reusable texts, LMCache can reuse the KV caches of any reused text"
" (not necessarily prefix) in any serving engine instance. It thus reduces"
" prefill delay, i.e., time to first token (TTFT), as well as saves the "
"precious GPU cycles and memory."
msgstr "LMCache 允许 LLM 仅对每个文本进行一次 Prefill。通过存储所有可重用文本的 KV Cache，LMCache 可以在任何服务引擎实例中重用任何重用文本的 KV Cache（不一定是前缀）。因此，它减少了 Prefill 延迟，即首次令牌时间 (TTFT)，并节省了宝贵的 GPU 周期和内存。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"By combining LMCache with vLLM, LMCache achieves 3-10x delay savings and "
"GPU cycle reduction in many LLM use cases, including multi-round QA and "
"RAG."
msgstr "通过将 LMCache 与 vLLM 结合，LMCache 在许多 LLM 用例中实现了 3-10 倍的延迟节省和显存周期减少，包括多轮问答和 RAG。"

